    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="carshowcase.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar.ejs') %>
    <!--Carousel-->
    <div id="main-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-pause="false">
        
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active c-item">
            <img src="homepage_carousel/img.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="..." data-bs-interval="500">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item c-item">
            <img src="homepage_carousel/img2.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="..." data-bs-interval="500">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item c-item">
            <img src="homepage_carousel/img3.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="..."data-bs-interval="500">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item c-item">
            <img src="homepage_carousel/img4.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="..."data-bs-interval="500">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item c-item">
            <img src="homepage_carousel/img5.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="..."data-bs-interval="500">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-text-overlay">
            <h1 class="carousel-title">About Us</h1>
            <hr class="carousel-hr">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="car-wrapper" id="about-wrapper">

      <div class="car-box-right" id="about-box">
        <div>

          <h2 class="car-box-right-title"><img class="info-icon" src="logos/info.svg" alt="">History</h2>
          <hr>
          <p class="car-box-right-text about-text">The Swansea University Race Engineering Team is a diverse group of 
            driven students who work together throughout the year to build a Formula style car.
          </p>
          <p class="car-box-right-text about-text"> From the first design to the manufacturing and procurement of parts, students prepare to present their 
            car to a panel of judges at the Silverstone during the Formula Student Competition.
          </p>
          <p class="car-box-right-text about-text">
              The competitive nature of such an event pushes students to apply what they learn in their respective 
              courses in a stressful scenario in hopes of performing and reaching their potential.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="car-box-right" id="about-box">
        <div>
          <h2 class="car-box-right-title"><img class="info-icon" src="logos/vision.svg" alt="">Vision</h2>
          <hr>
          <p class="car-box-right-text about-text">The Swansea University Race Engineering Team has been working hard for 
            the past 5 years to come back from its pre-pandemic strength. Being one of three Welsh teams participating in 
            the competition meant that not being able to come to competition with a working car has made us eager to perform. 
            With the current team being driven and close to a working car we are excited to see what this year brings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>